## Quick Reference

### Atomic Design

```
Atoms → Molecules → Organisms → Templates → Pages

Atoms:      Button, Input, Icon, Label
Molecules:  SearchBar (Input + Button + Icon)
Organisms:  Header (Logo + Nav + SearchBar)
Templates:  Page layout structure
Pages:      Actual page with real content
```

