## Accessibility (a11y)

### Color Contrast

- Normal text: 4.5:1 ratio minimum
- Large text: 3:1 ratio minimum
- Use tools like WebAIM Contrast Checker

### Interactive Elements

- Minimum touch target: 44x44px
- Focus states visible
- Keyboard navigable

